<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Account Suspension Notice - Codeforces</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #dc3545;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    .warning-box {
      background-color: #fff3f4;
      border: 1px solid #dc3545;
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8em;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      color: white;
      background-color: #dc3545;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Account Suspension Notice</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear {{email}},</p>
    
    <div class="warning-box">
      <p><strong>Your Codeforces account has been suspended effective from {{banDate}}.</strong></p>
    </div>

    <p>This action has been taken due to:</p>
    <p><strong>{{reason}}</strong></p>

    <p>Duration of suspension: {{duration}}</p>
    
    <p>This suspension means you will not be able to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Participate in contests</li>
      <li>Submit solutions to problems</li>
      <li>Post in forums or comments</li>
      <li>Rate or vote on content</li>
    </ul>

    {{#if appealAllowed}}
    <p>If you believe this decision was made in error, you may appeal this suspension by:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Reviewing our <a href="{{rulesUrl}}">community guidelines</a></li>
      <li>Submitting an appeal through our <a href="{{appealUrl}}">appeal form</a></li>
    </ol>
    {{/if}}

    <p>Please note that repeated violations of our community guidelines may result in permanent account termination.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Codeforces. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>